text: Ropicomimus vitticollis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1953. It is known from Papua New Guinea.BioLib.cz - Ropicomimus vitticollis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1953
title: Ropicomimus vitticollis
